{"tid":5854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"婦人逛夜市　慘遭空拍機突襲險失明","createTime":"2016-11-27T05:46:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T06:16:41.000Z","uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a59aebffad26e96001b0b53c8a9204e9564673a","tid":5854,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"空拍機在台灣掀起熱潮，但現在又傳出劃傷民眾的消息。1名婦人到寧夏夜市逛街，沒想到無人空拍機就像血滴子一樣朝著她墜落，婦人當場頭部和手臂血流如注。<br />\n<br />\n寧夏夜市有民眾被無人空拍機割傷，台北市議員顏若芳接獲陳情，指1名婦人在人潮眾多的寧夏夜市逛街，沒想到無人空拍機疑似因為操作不慎，就像血滴子一樣朝婦人臉部砸過來，害她差點失明。<br />\n<br />\n婦人被砸當下血流如注，疑似因為用手臂保護頭部，導致手臂上還留著2道至少5公分以上的傷痕，而婦人的臉、眉毛上頭、眼睛周圍也因此破相，傷痕累累，甚至就差一點點還可能因此失明，後果難以想像。<br />\n<br />\n只是逛個夜市，怎麼會禍從天降？議員顏若芳痛批，台灣關於空拍機的規範是25公斤以下交由地方政府制定，像這種無人空拍機若是再無完善規定及配套，恐怕會讓民眾的安全陷入隱憂。（整理：實習編輯林奇樺）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=202053\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D202053&d=8jSl%2F07Erb5WLRU5GsSSW8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=1a9189dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D202053&h=a8808dd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=202053</a>"},{"pid":"e727bd119475a9fcd38db6989053ee158bda29d0","tid":5854,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"032c40ad0661446f9c1251d93a0457bc6aecab73","tid":5854,"uid":13174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210de93d2cee4aeb45f98d0da1ef6bcd4ab14cc7","tid":5854,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"D撚樣比細路當遙控飛機咁玩 行過都走快兩步"},{"pid":"1c1a38ead56b107fa5e31cffd6aebf2f5c4bf2b5","tid":5854,"uid":25721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5f8268e197734e2998f85bee4e5db2877e27db","tid":5854,"uid":2674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T06:16:41.000Z","msg":"美國都好似有幾單"}]}